  "narrative": {
    "headline": "Peak chaos \u2014 spans blown, VP exits, role drift widespread",
    "body": "David Park, the VP Engineering hired the previous year, exits after 12 months \u2014 an expensive misfire. Span of control is still manageable but role drift is widespread: Jasmine Osei manages five designers with an IC4 title, Gabby Torres effectively runs all of Operations as an IC3. Sophie Laurent (Sr PM) and Thomas Kirk (Content) depart. Adrienne flags structural concerns informally for the first time. The Customer Insight duplication compounds.",
    "odHealth": "At Risk",
    "odNote": "VP Engineering misfire resolved but trust in external senior hires dented. Role titles not matching actual scope. Customer Insight teams siloed. First informal warnings about structural drift.",
    "keyEvents": [
      "David Park (VP Engineering) exits after 12 months \u2014 misfire acknowledged",
      "Three heads at 9 direct reports each \u2014 over threshold",
      "Sophie Laurent (Sr PM) and Thomas Kirk (Content Manager) both depart",
      "Adrienne Cole informally flags span of control concerns to CEO"
    ]
